      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:14",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "很严肃",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:15",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我不会否定别人的痛苦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:15",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "每个人对痛苦的耐受都不一样，不能因为我觉得别人的痛苦轻，我就说那不是痛苦",
