      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:19",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "确实",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:19",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "讲究一个留白的艺术，这真的算我的职业病",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:20",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "思维绕来又绕去",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:20",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我是想说，如果我觉得你的状态很糟糕，我胡乱说话可能会刺激你",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:21",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "那我就会一直顺着你说，不管那个东西，我是不是真的这么觉得",
